The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 58

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

It's a sprint to the finish line as both houses complete their backyards. The judges look over the entire houses and give their final scores of the season, this time to determine which teams get an extra $10,000 off their reserve prices.
